text: Nihsansaya, sarvasrestha allahane tumhala aneka yud'dhabhumita vijaya pradana kela ahe ani hunaina-yud'dhacya divasihi, jevha tumhala apalya jasta sankhyebaddala ghamenda hoti, parantu asane tumhala kahica labha jhala nahi, tathapi dharati apali visalata (balagata) asatanahi tumacyasathi sankucita (tanga) jhali, maga tumhi patha phiravuna dura palale
